com.viaoa.object

Class OAObjectInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.viaoa.object.OAObjectInfo

  • public class OAObjectInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    OAObjectInfo contains information about an OAObject. This includes object id, links to other objects, calculated properties.

    Note: this will be replaced by the com.viaoa.model Classes

    For more information about this package, see documentation.
